At OUT OF THE ORDINARY (and our brands), accessible from https://outoftheordinary.io, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors and users of our applications.
This policy describes how OUT OF THE ORDINARY including its brand (later referred to as “we”, “us”, “our”, “OUT OF THE ORDINARY Sp. z o. o.”, „OUT OF THE ORDINARY”) and its third party marketing and advertising partners collect, use, process and share information about you.
This Privacy Policy applies to all of our products, used on any accessible platform (such as PCs, mobile devices, other). It also applies to our Marketing and Advertising activities on all platforms and other services that we may provide to your infrequently. In this document we refer to our games, websites, marketing and advertising activities and other services collectively as our “Services”.
Using our Services
By downloading, accessing and/or playing our games, or interacting with our websites or other Services you agree to the collection and use of your information in accordance with this Privacy Policy, emphasizing granting a consent to us and our advertising partners in order to use of your data for targeted advertising purposes as described in the following sections of this Privacy Policy. Those sections also explain how you can withhold or withdraw your consent to the use of your data for targeted advertising purposes. If you have any other concerns about providing information to us or it being used as described in this Privacy Policy you should not use our games or other Services.
Analytics
At OUT OF THE ORDINARY, our main objective is to provide our community with best possible gaming experience ever created! To do so, we use 3-rd party analytics solutions such as
Facebook Analytics
,
Unity Analytics
,
Game Analytics
and
Google Analytics
. With your prior consent, we are likely to collect some crucial information, which would allow us to better address your needs and expectation, this data can be as follows: IDFA publicity identifiers (for IOS devices) and GAID (for Android devices) Data pertaining to your activities on our applications and notably the way in which you interact with our applications (for instance, how and when you use our applications) and with the publicities we display (for instance, time spent on these, potential clicks) Keep in mind that during iterative development, Analytics Services are one of the vital parts of our products – we will include information about product being in iterative development stage to address that if using our product you give your consent to have analytical data collected and analyzed by our company and other parties in cooperation.
Marketing
We and our third party partners use information collected about you to send you suitable form of marketing communications about other our product and Services, which will be based upon your interests. You may see ads containing other our products, see them on our website and other Services. In any time you can opt out by removing any of our products and sending us an appropriate email to unsubscribe from receiving any interest-base advertisements via
contact@outoftheordinary.io
.
Advertising
Our Services may include advertising for third party products and services. By accepting this Privacy Policy and downloading or continuing to play our games our use our Services, unless you opt out of interest-based advertising from third party providers, more information about this process will be included down below, you consent to us and our advertising partners collecting and using information about you to improve advertising, targeting and measurement systems so that we can show you relevant third party ads in our games. Any details about gathered information is broadly pointed in Privacy Policy specific to third party provider of interest.
